The Process Heat the extra virgin olive oil in a skillet. Add tofu, spices, and hot sauce and cook for a few minutes until heated through. Add salt to taste. (Cook ground chicken or lean beef with the same spices as tofu, but allow 10 more minutes). Arrange tomatoes, avocado, cabbage, onions, and limes on a platter. Heat tortillas. Assemble the taco with your favorite ingredients.